<p>If by &quot;make it begin&quot; you mean you're not sure about how to start writing an interview log, you can look at existing SCP articles for examples. If you're not sure about the coding, the &quot;Templates&quot; tab of the How to Write an SCP Guide has a simple coding example you can use.</p>
