			<div class="content" id="post-content-3638748">
									

<p>All that went through my head the first two times that I read this was this: Be specific, use grammar, make the dots connect, make readers understand why the special containment procedures is how it is, give the SCP a little bit of a story, don't just say it does something, don't make it short, and really that's all I can remember. I've attempted creating my own once, and oh boy did it fail. What am I missing?</p>

