<blockquote>
<p>I've attempted creating my own once, and oh boy did it fail. What am I missing?</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Getting feedback on your drafts before posting. As mentioned in the 7th bullet point under the &quot;Developing Thoughts&quot; tab. Getting feedback on a SCP before posting is generally one of the most important steps- it gives you a chance to see where you're making mistakes and how to correct them.</p>
<p>Otherwise&#8230; well, you've already seen what generally happens if you post without getting feedback first.</p>

